text: The Mercedes-Benz EQS SUV is a fully-electric, full-sized luxury crossover SUV produced by luxury brand Mercedes-Benz since 2022. It has an optional choice of second and third row seating and goes by the model code 'X296'. ==Other websites== * EQS SUV Category:2020s automobiles Category:Sport utility vehicles
